channel.title: [HELP] Error
channel.description:
I'm currently trying to add an ipban command to my server and i keep getting this error
[code]client.java:163: not a statement Public Void;processReport;String msg; { ^ 1 error Finished! Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Please help.
Early thanks, Undernoob

item.title: [HELP] Error
item.dc:creator: @slomifier slomifier
item.description:
@slomifier wrote:

umm, probably because java is case sensitive

void = Infinite Nothingness, and Returns “Nothing”
Void = An Undefined Variable

easy mistake, but should be obvious
